{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, hey, who's-- later on, I understood what he said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, why are you crying, in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I started talking, and he speaks half Yiddish, half German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he tells me that he is-- he is an Austrian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's talking about 1918, the monarchy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he starts to explain to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, they don't-- they don't speak to you because you don't speak Yiddish, and they don't trust you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you're a [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, what is this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he explains to me in as short as he can that when the people-- the Polish Jews-- came to Austria in 1914, '15, '16, '18, whatever, '19, '20, they were looked upon by the so-called old Austrians-- which were the first, the second, or third generation-- as dirty and unedu-- uneducated and filthy.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were nothing, and they're this and that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, so I [? have ?] [? to? ?] I said, I don't know about that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said I never saw or heard, when I grew up, that this guy was from here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had so many Czechs down there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was Hans and Josef and [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Karly ?] and who knows what, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyhow, what shall I do, I said to the guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, you have to-- how did he say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Du musst lernen mamaloshen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You have to learn mamaloshen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now I don't know what is mamaloshen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says, Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "How do you learn the language?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said, that's very simple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He said, you have to learn how to swear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I said, swear what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, just make up words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he gave me a couple of samples, which I used first, and then I elaborate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four weeks later, I was perfect.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
